ygData.messageBody:
so i got sick of dying in cazic thule tonite, (twice for a loss of a bubble
of exp, so i onlt netted one bubble). i went and made an erudite female
enchantress by the name of Qoronette. it's cute, since my enchanter is
Qorona. for the life of me, i cant remember how i made it through the first
8 levels. this should be fun. =)

Qorona Mindbender of the Volition Guild, 22nd lvl enchanter on Cazic-Thule
